00:48:54.639 --> 00:49:01.080
What reprex does and don't document outlines various ways of doing this.

00:49:01.080 --> 00:49:04.840
For example, deput is a great function.

00:49:04.840 --> 00:49:10.520
If you have a slightly awkward object and you simply cannot make your point without

00:49:10.520 --> 00:49:17.320
