But what I will say, the slide that I skipped over, what actually happens, so currently

00:50:30.080 --> 00:50:38.479
reprex works by dumping your R code into a templated R script.

00:50:38.479 --> 00:50:46.800
And I have contemplated revisiting this and dumping it into an R markdown file.

